      <title>斯里兰卡左翼领导人面临改变国际货币基金组织协议的严峻考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/sri-lanka-s-leftist-leader-faces-tough-test-to-alter-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡新总统上任后，肩负着为仍受该国史上最严重经济危机影响的民众提供救济的使命。现在最难的部分来了：让贷款人参与进来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/sri-lanka-s-leftist-leader-faces-tough-test-to-alter-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:15:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道日本军舰首次穿越台湾海峡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-warship-sails-through-taiwan-strait-in-a-first-nhk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，日本周三派出军舰穿越台湾海峡，这是日本二战后重建武装力量以来首次，表明其愿意在地区安全问题上采取更强硬的立场，此举可能会激怒中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-warship-sails-through-taiwan-strait-in-a-first-nhk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:25:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
